![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7096617b-ed4f-44f3-aa10-0aff4bc4c7e0/e265.jpg)

It looks like the DC Universe is set for a reboot and they aren't alone. We'll be getting new versions of the Fantastic Four, Blade, and the X-Men soon, which means brand-new actors playing familiar roles. Before things change, let's look back at some of the best casting choices in comic book media history! Join as on this walk down memory lane as we give flowers to some of the greats to ever do it!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

